 🤖 AI ChatBot using Java

📌 Project Overview

This project is a Java-based AI ChatBot developed using Java Swing as part of the CodeAlpha Java Development Internship.

 🚀 Features

* Java Swing GUI
* Rule-based chatbot
* Interactive conversation
* FAQ responses
* User-friendly interface

🛠 Technologies Used

* Java
* Java Swing
* AWT
* Event Handling
* Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

 ▶️ How to Run

1. Open the project in Eclipse.
2. Run `ChatBotGUI.java`.
3. Start chatting with the bot.

